Directed by Sujana Rao

Written by Sai Madhav Burra. Sujana Rao

Star Agastya .Palak Aggarwal .Alakananda .Charu Haasan .Hemaani .Vasu Inturi . Priyanka Jawalkar (Zara). Shiva Kandukuri (Ali). Meka Rama Krishna ((as Ramakrishna Meka)).Kakinada Laxmi .T. Manu. Nithya Menen (Shailaputri Devi). Nehanth. Chakri Ntv. Devi Ntv. Vamsi Penumarthi. Bhanu Prakash (Bhanu).Bhanu Prakash. Ravi Prakash (Police Officer Raghuram).Prameela. Priya. Venki Pushadapu. Gopal Rao. Sravana Sandhya. Aaron Sankla. Shriya Saran (Kamala). Bitthiri Sathi. Bongu Sathi. Sreeja. Suhas. Sreeja Suma. Suneetha. Silver Suresh. Chelly Swapna. Sanjay Swaroop. Teeksha. Subba Rao Vepada (Cricket Coach). Aman Vikyath

Language Telugu

Producers Ramesh Karutoori. Venki Pushadapu. Ch. Chandra Sekhar. Gnanashekar V.S.

Production Kali Productions. Kria Film
